Job_Description:
Duties
As a Management and Program Analyst supporting the Chief of Staff some of your specific duties will include:
Data analysis and the ability to identify, analyze, recognize accurate/inaccurate or questionable content;
Identifying discrepancies in monthly status reports;
Coordinating with internal departments to oversee completion of a wide variety of projects;
Reviewing policies and directives and recommending changes if necessary.

Duties
As a Computer Scientist within the Geologic Hazards Science Center, some of your specific duties will include:
Writing code to allocate and configure cloud resources in AWS (or similar provider);
Writing code to load, update and modify databases using SQL or similar;
Writing public facing, web-based applications using modern frameworks such as Angular or similar;
Communicating effectively with their supervisor, their colleagues, and stakeholders.
